creator: HeyExpert
descriptionHtml:
HeyExpert is a unique platform that connects you with highly valued experts across a wide variety of fields. Whether you’re seeking short term advice on a particular issue, or are looking to develop on a personal or professional level over the long term, our experts are here to provide valuable guidance, from the comfort of your own home!

Download the app now and begin to explore our many niches.
Find an expert that meets your particular needs. You can search for an expert within various niches or by keywords.
Connect with your chosen expert
Enjoy unlimited messaging with your expert for the duration of your subscription period.


Popular niches include:
- Parenting
- Career Coaching
- Mental Health & Addiction counseling
- Personal Fitness, Diet & Nutrition
- Financial Planning
- Life Coaching & Personal development
- E-Commerce
- Small Business Management

Want to Join our Team?

If you’re licensed in your field or have extensive experience and are a trusted professional, join our team of experts: https://join-us.hey-expert.com

If you want to head a niche and be in charge of recruiting experts and generating traffic, join our team of niche managers: https://join-us.hey-expert.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: The new version enables one on one video chats with your expert. Schedule your live session via chat.
